Class EmployeeHashTable

  • java.lang.Object
    • EmployeeHashTable
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class EmployeeHashTable
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    A open hashing/closed addressing hash table class for EmployeeInfo objects. Contains methods for adding and removing EmployeeInfo objects from the hash table, as well as a method for displaying its contents.
    See Also:
